    "## 5. Practical Tips and Best Practices\n",
    "\n",
    "### Choosing Architecture\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "Decision Tree:\n",
    "├── Need future context?\n",
    "│   ├── Yes → Bidirectional\n",
    "│   └── No → Unidirectional\n",
    "├── Complex patterns?\n",
    "│   ├── Yes → Stacked (2-3 layers)\n",
    "│   └── No → Single layer\n",
    "├── Long sequences?\n",
    "│   ├── Yes → LSTM\n",
    "│   └── No → GRU (faster)\n",
    "└── Limited resources?\n",
    "    ├── Yes → GRU, fewer layers\n",
    "    └── No → LSTM, more layers\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### Common Mistakes\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Forgetting return_sequences=True**\n",
    "   - Required for stacked RNNs\n",
    "   - Only last layer should have return_sequences=False\n",
    "\n",
    "2. **Too many layers**\n",
    "   - 2-3 layers usually sufficient\n",
    "   - More layers = more overfitting risk\n",
    "\n",
    "3. **No dropout**\n",
    "   - Always use dropout between layers\n",
    "   - Typical values: 0.2-0.5\n",
    "\n",
    "4. **Wrong bidirectional usage**\n",
    "   - Don't use for real-time prediction\n",
    "   - Requires full sequence available\n",
    "\n",
    "### Hyperparameter Guidelines\n",
    "\n",
    "| Parameter | Typical Range | Notes |\n",
    "|-----------|---------------|-------|\n",
    "| **Hidden units** | 32-512 | Start with 64-128 |\n",
    "| **Layers** | 1-3 | 2 is common |\n",
    "| **Dropout** | 0.2-0.5 | Higher for larger models |\n",
    "| **Embedding dim** | 50-300 | 128 is good default |\n",
    "| **Batch size** | 32-128 | Larger for longer sequences |"
   ]
